{"sn24.13:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 24.13 ","sn24.13:0.2":"1. Sotapattivagga ","sn24.13:0.3":"Tamjivamtamsariramsutta ","sn24.13:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn24.13:1.2":"“Kismim nu kho, bhikkhave, sati, kim upadaya, kim abhinivissa evam ditthi uppajjati: ","sn24.13:1.3":"‘tam jivam tam sariran’”ti? ","sn24.13:1.4":"“Bhagavammulaka no, bhante, dhamma …pe… ","sn24.13:1.5":"niyato sambodhiparayano”ti. ","sn24.13:1.6":"Terasamam. "}